Greenbriar.    Fort Randolph. on Ohio at mouth              |
                 Gr. Kanhaway                         200.  |
               Kellys on the Gr. Kanhaway 20.    }         |
                 m. abov. mouth of Elk.           }         | Greenbriar  22
               Little meadows. on waters of Gr.   }         |
                 briar abt 30. or 40. mi. from    }   100   |
                 warm springs, more to Northward  }         |
               Sinks on Gr. Kanhaway opposite     }         |
